OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsiders changing Mental Capacity Act
OL,6,FCare Minister Stephen Kinnock held a
OL,7,Fmeeting with cross-party MPs and Fiona
OL,8,FLaskaris, a mother who has spent years
OL,9,Ffighting for the change in law that
OL,10,Fshe believes could have saved her
OL,11,Fautistic son.
OL,13,FChristopher Laskaris was 24 years old
OL,14,Fwhen he was murdered in 2016 by a
OL,15,Fconvicted criminal who had been
OL,16,Fexploiting him.
