OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsiders changing Mental Capacity Act
OL,6,FSince ITV News aired Fiona's story and
OL,7,Fthe prime minister's subsequent pledge
OL,8,Fin the Commons to "look into" the law
OL,9,Fchange, we have been contacted by
OL,10,Fother families also battling to get
OL,11,Fmental capacity assessments. Due to
OL,12,Fthe issue being underreported, many
OL,13,Fsaid they didn't realise they were not
OL,14,Falone in their fight.
OL,16,FOne mother said she "sobbed
OL,17,Funcontrollably", adding: "I thought,
OL,18,Fthere are other people like us."
