OL,6,FWhat is the Mental Capacity Act and
OL,7,Fhow could the law change?
OL,9,FThe Mental Capacity Act was introduced
OL,10,Fin 2005 in a bid to minimise the
OL,11,Fnumber of vulnerable adults being
OL,12,Fdetained unreasonably and
OL,13,Findefinitely, and to give them more
OL,14,Fautonomy over their own care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
