OL,6,FTheir insistence that they can cope is
OL,7,Foften taken at face value without
OL,8,Fconsidering their past history and
OL,9,Frelatives' concerns. This means that -
OL,10,Fas in Christopher Laskaris' case -
OL,11,Fthey are left without the support they
OL,12,Fneed.
