OL,4,Cconsiders changing Mental Capacity Act
OL,6,FFiona and three MPs - the former
OL,7,Fhealth secretary Jeremy Hunt
OL,8,F(Conservatives), Chris Coghlan (Lib
OL,9,FDems) and Jake Richards (Labour) - are
OL,10,Fcalling for an amendment to the Mental
OL,11,FCapacity Act to ensure family members'
OL,12,Fviews are taken into account when
OL,13,Fdeciding if someone needs a mental
