OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsiders changing Mental Capacity Act
OL,6,FBarrister Ian Brownhill, who's a
OL,7,Fspecialist in mental capacity, said
OL,8,Fdecisions around capacity are a
OL,9,Fproblem the courts see time and again.
OL,11,F"The issues are vast," he said.
OL,12,F"Sometimes it can be something like a
OL,13,Fpredatory marriage where somebody
OL,14,Ftargets someone because they want to
OL,15,Fget access to their finances. In other
OL,16,Fcases it's more insipid - it might be
OL,17,Fsomething like a drug dealer, or
OL,18,Fcuckooing, and things like that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
