OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsiders changing Mental Capacity Act
OL,6,FParveen's son would spend day and
OL,7,Fnight in bed not eating or drinking
OL,8,Fand fought for years to try to get him
OL,9,Fa mental capacity assessment in the
OL,10,Fhopes that it would get him the help
OL,11,Fhe desperately needed.
OL,13,F"They were assuming he's got capacity
OL,14,Fand therefore, it's his reasoned
OL,15,Fdecision - if he doesn't want help, he
OL,16,Fdoesn't want support, that's fine by
OL,17,Fus," she said.
