OL,6,F"Even though I was providing evidence
OL,7,Fthat that's not the case. He's not
OL,8,Fwell. He doesn't understand the
OL,9,Fconsequences of this. There's no way
OL,10,Fon earth he would just lie in bed day
OL,11,Fand night like this deteriorating of
OL,12,Fhis own choice.
OL,14,F"I genuinely believed that he would
