OL,3,C'There are others like us': Government
OL,4,Cconsiders changing Mental Capacity Act
OL,6,FShe added: "As I was reading this
OL,7,F(Fiona's) story... I thought, there
OL,8,Fare other people like us. This tragedy
OL,9,Fhas happened and services could've
OL,10,Fstopped this from happening. Fiona had
OL,11,Fraised this time and time again, like
OL,12,FI have over 12 years for my son."
OL,14,F'I'm hopeful this terrible thing that
OL,15,Fhappened to Christopher can bring
OL,16,Fsomething positive'
OL,18,FFiona and MP Chris Coghlan remain
OL,19,Fhopeful following the meeting with the
OL,20,Fgovernment and await to hear next
OL,21,Fsteps.
